about.summary: Produces LaTeX code, HTML/CSS code and ASCII text for well-formatted tables that hold  regression analysis results from several models side-by-side, as well as summary statistics.

name: r-stargazer
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '5.2.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-stargazer
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/stargazer_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/stargazer/stargazer_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 70eb4a13a6ac1bfb35af07cb8a63d501ad38dfd9817fc3fba6724260b23932de

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('stargazer')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('stargazer')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=stargazer
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Produces LaTeX code, HTML/CSS code and ASCII text for well-formatted tables that hold  regression
    analysis results from several models side-by-side, as well as summary statistics.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - xhochy

# Description: Produces LaTeX code, HTML/CSS code and ASCII text for well-formatted tables that hold  regression analysis results from several models side-by-side, as well as summary statistics.
